OL,6,FA Ballymena bed and breakfast manager
OL,7,Fwas fatally stabbed in March 2020
OL,8,Fwhile he was on the phone with the
OL,9,FPSNI reporting another stabbing, a
OL,10,Fcourt heard today.
OL,12,FInayat Shah ran the Traveller's Rest
OL,13,Fon the Galgorm Road in the Co Antrim
OL,14,Ftown.
OL,16,FHe was stabbed 55 times in his
OL,17,Fbusiness in on March 21st 2020.
