OL,6,FMichael Lenaghan, with an address at
OL,7,FGalgorm Road, initially denied
OL,8,Fmurdering the 67-year old, but then
OL,9,Fpleaded guilty before the case went to
OL,10,Ftrial.
OL,12,FFamily members were in attendance at
OL,13,FBelfast Crown Court as the gruesome
OL,14,Fdetails of what happened to their
OL,15,F"kind and charitable" relative were
OL,16,Frevealed.
