OL,6,FDuring the plea hearing, it emerged
OL,7,Fthat prior to killing Mr Shah,
OL,8,FLenaghan had attacked another resident
OL,9,Fwith a knife and made a death threat
OL,10,Fto another guest.
OL,12,FJudge Patricia Smyth was told that Mr
OL,13,FShah was in the process of reporting
OL,14,Fthis to emergency services when he was
OL,15,Fapproached by Lenaghan, who was still
OL,16,Farmed with a knife.
