OL,6,FAn eye witness reported seeing
OL,7,FLenaghan gesturing and shouting
OL,8,Faggressively, being taken to the
OL,9,Fground, and being struck repeatedly by
OL,10,Fhim.
OL,12,FMr Magee KC, prosecuting, said that
OL,13,Fthe "chilling and devastating attack"
OL,14,Fwas recorded on the call.
OL,16,FHe said: "Mr Shah pleaded with the
OL,17,Fdefendant and offered to give him
OL,18,Fmoney but the defendant shouted at him
OL,19,Fsaying 'you're dead, you're dead,
OL,20,Ftalking to the police about me, you're
OL,21,Fdead, you're dead', you're dead."
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G4/10
