OL,6,FCovered in blood, he told the resident
OL,7,Fhe threatened earlier that day "you'll
OL,8,Fend up like Shah there, dead in the
OL,9,Fstreet."
OL,11,FA short time after this he was
OL,12,Fapproached by police and said: "That
OL,13,Fthing is in the alley. I did it. It's
OL,14,Fme you're looking for."
OL,16,FWhen arrested for murder, Lenaghan
OL,17,Fasked "is he dead?" and when told this
OL,18,Fwas the case, he replied "f*****g
OL,19,Fgood".
