OL,6,FHe was overheard by Mr Shah's daughter
OL,7,Fshouting "happy days."
OL,9,FHe was aggressive and abusive to
OL,10,Fofficers and to custody staff at the
OL,11,FPSNI station and during a police
OL,12,Finterview, he gave a largely 'no
OL,13,Fcomment' response.
OL,15,FWith an address as Galgorm Road in
OL,16,FBallymena, Lenaghan later admitted
OL,17,Fmurdering Mr Shah on March 21, 2020.
OL,18,FHe also admitted wounding one fellow
OL,19,Fresident and threatening to kill
OL,20,Fanother on the same date.
