OL,6,FBranding the fatal attack on Mr Shah
OL,7,Fas "callous" and "gratuitous" and one
OL,8,Fwhere "wanton violence was inflicted
OL,9,Fon the victim", the prosecutor told
OL,10,FJudge Smyth that Lenaghan had a
OL,11,Frelevant criminal record for violent
OL,12,Foffences in Northern Ireland, Scotland
OL,13,Fand England.
OL,15,FA defence barrister said his client
OL,16,Fsuffered from an acute and complex
OL,17,Fpersonality disorder which resulted in
OL,18,Floss of control.
